1. Ne mogu si *priuštiti* luksuzni život. (I can't afford a luxurious lifestyle.)
2. Oni su sebi *priuštili* skupocjeni automobil. (They treated themselves to an expensive car.)
3. Ako nešto *priuštimo* sebi, onda to treba biti zasluženo. (If we indulge ourselves in something, it should be well-deserved.)
4. Želim si *priuštiti* putovanje u Japan. (I want to treat myself to a trip to Japan.)
5. Oni će si *priuštiti* veliku proslavu za svoj godišnjak braka. (They will celebrate their wedding anniversary with a big party.)
6. Nažalost, ne mogu si *priuštiti* da kupim taj novi televizor. (Unfortunately, I can't afford to buy that new TV.)
7. *Priuštiti* si nešto nije uvijek materijalne prirode. (Treating yourself to something isn't always materialistic.)
8. Mislim da si to ne možemo *priuštiti* u ovom trenutku. (I think we can't afford that right now.)
9. Oni su *priuštili* sebi opuštajući dan u spa centru. (They indulged themselves with a relaxing day at the spa.)
10. Ne treba *si priuštiti* stvari koje ne možemo platiti. (We shouldn't treat ourselves to things we can't afford.)